Class NodeMaxHeap

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.wmich.cs3310.ddarcy.NodeMaxHeap

  • public class NodeMaxHeap
extends java.lang.Object
    CLASS DESCRIPTION: This class is a node based max-heap. It uses the attributes below to create a binary search tree with many different methods which include insert, the constructor, search, get methods, set methods, etc.
    Author:
    Daniel Darcy
